title: Know What To Ignore | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Know What To Ignore | Joel Osteen
description:
We have to be selective about what we give our time and attention to. If a battle is not between you and your God-given destiny, it’s a battle you should ignore. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
